node.text: doggy appreciation post 🥺😭❤️ these three are so all unique and they each bring their own totally different personality into my house and it’s hilarious. I love themmm and I’m so glad so many of you do too!!! I feel like they’re everyone’s favorite part of my stories 😂 if you could only boop ONE of them on the nose…… which one would you choose? don’t worry, I won’t tell 🤫💁🏼‍♀️
